# Contract-First Prompting (2026)

## Purpose
Convert ambiguous requests into a signed-off execution contract before implementation.

## Required contract fields
- Objective
- In-scope / out-of-scope
- Inputs, dependencies, assumptions
- Observable acceptance criteria
- Risks and fallback strategy
- Explicit approval gate

## Interaction policy
- Ask clarifying questions in priority order.
- Summarize resolved decisions after each major turn.
- Do not proceed to execution without explicit approval.
